Write a program to print the following pattern based an input n
For example:
Input 
3
Result
1
2 3
4 5 6

Solution:
//Java

import java.util.*;
public class pattern_incre1 {
    public static void main(String[]ar){
        Scanner a=new Scanner(System.in);
        int in=a.nextInt();
        int co=1;
        for(int i=0;i<in;i++){
            for(int j=0;j<=i;j++){
                System.out.print(co+++" ");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }
}


